Package strategy.implementations

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicStrategy
    This abstract class provides methods and fields that are needed for almost every good mastermind strategy and thus decreases code duplication.
    Knuth
    Strategy that uses the worst case algorithm also known as the "Knuth Algorithm" after its creator Donald Knuth.
    Random
    A strategy that always guesses randomly.
    Simple
    Class Simple strategy.
